Symbol.Script_2D:
mul2 -1,-1 !project2 1, 90, 1 del 1
add2 0,1 !project2 2, 270, 1 del 1
add2 a+2,1 !project2 1, 180, 1 del 1
!fragment2 1,1
pen cul_line set fill fill_type
mul2 1,(1-2*(1-WIDO_REVEAL_SIDE)) add2 -a/2,0 add2 0,WALL_THICKNESS/2 mul2 1,(1-2*(1-WIDO_REVEAL_SIDE)) add2 0,-y_rama/2 GOSUB "rame" add2 x_rama-offset_pliere,0 GOSUB "pliere" del 1
add2 -0.03,0 GOSUB "handles" del 1 del 1 del 1 del 1 DEL 1
END
"rame":
rama_stanga="tip_rama1" rama_dreapta="tip_rama1" rama_sus="tip_rama1" prag="tip_rama1"
l_prism=y_rama y_prism=x_rama y_prism1=y_prism-0.03 g_profil=0.002
offx1=0.005 gx_mij=0.045 gy_mij=0.015
gx2_mij=0.008 gy2_mij=0.02
mul2 -1,1 rot2 90 if (index_2d_level=1) then GOSUB "contur rama simpla" endif if (index_2d_level=2) then GOSUB "contur profil Uu" endif poly2_B nsp/3,1+2+4,fill_p,fill_b,get(nsp) del 1 del 1 add2 a,0 mul2 1,1 rot2 90 if (index_2d_level=1) then GOSUB "contur rama simpla2" endif if (index_2d_level=2) then GOSUB "contur profil Uu2" endif poly2_B nsp/3,1+2+4,fill_p,fill_b,get(nsp) del 1 del 1 del 1
RETURN
!!!__-
"handles":
add2 x_rama,0
hotline2 0,0,l1_pliat,0
unID=0
unID=unID+1
hotspot2 0, 0, unID, l1_pliat, 1+128
unID=unID+1
hotspot2 l1_pliat, 0, unID, l1_pliat, 2
unID=unID+1
hotspot2 -1, 0, unID, l1_pliat, 3
del 1
RETURN
"balama usa":
IF index_2d_level=2 THEN add2 0,-0.011 circle2 0,0,0.018/2 del 1 ENDIF
RETURN
"balama usa2":
IF index_2d_level=2 THEN add2 -0.018*sin(u_diag)/2,-y_profil_usa-0.011 circle2 0,0,0.018/2 del 1 ENDIF
RETURN
!!!_--PLIERE
"pliere":
l_cadru=x_panou1+0.005/2 l_usa = dx1_usa-0.002 kk = 0
FOR ll = 0 TO l1_pliat-0.03 STEP dx1_pliat
kk = kk + 1
mm = CEIL ( FRA ( kk / 2 ) )
add2 ll,0
IF mm THEN GOSUB "expresie usa impar"
ENDIF
IF NOT ( mm ) THEN
GOSUB "expresie usa par"
ENDIF
del 1
NEXT ll
RETURN
"expresie usa par":
add2 dx1_pliat-0.018*sin(u_diag)/2,0 mul2 -1,1 ROT2 (-u_diag)*rot_panou rot2 (-u_corectie-u_diff*sin(u_diag))*rot_panou if kk<n1 then !rect2 0,0,dx1_usa,0.05 GOSUB "door2" endif if kk=n1 then GOSUB "door4" endif del 1 del 1
del 1 del 1
RETURN
"expresie usa impar":
IF kk>1 AND kk<=n1 then GOSUB "balama usa" endif
!!____-BALAMA add2 0.018*sin(u_diag)/2,0 ROT2 (-u_diag)*rot_panou rot2 (-u_corectie-u_diff*sin(u_diag))*rot_panou if kk<n1 then !rect2 0,0,dx1_usa,0.05 GOSUB "door" endif if kk=n1 then GOSUB "door3" endif
if kk<n1 then add2 dx1_usa,0 mul2 1,-1 GOSUB "balama usa2" del 2 endif del 2 del 1
RETURN
"door2":
add2 l_usa,0 mul2 -1,1 GOSUB "door" del 1 del 1
RETURN
"door3":
!rect2 0,0,dx1_usa,g_usa
l1_prism=0.4 l2_prism=0.3 x_r_door=0.1 g_door=0.022 y1_prism=0.2 y2_prism=0.1 r_prism=0.003
l_prism=x_profil_usa g_profil=0.002 y_prism=y_profil_usa
IF (index_2d_level=1) THEN PUT 0,0,15, l_usa,0,15, l_usa,y_prism,15, 0,y_prism,15 poly2_B nsp/3,1+2+4,fill_p,fill_b,get(nsp) ENDIF
IF (index_2d_level=2) THEN add2 x_profil_usa,y_profil_usa/2 rot2 90 GOSUB "profil usa5 t" poly2_B nsp/3,1+2+4,fill_p,fill_b,get(nsp) del 1 del 1
y_prism=y_profil_usa+0.04
add2 l_usa-0.04-0.013,0 mul2 -1,1 add2 x_profil_usa,y_profil_usa/2 rot2 90 GOSUB "profil usa7 t" poly2_B nsp/3,1+2+4,fill_p,fill_b,get(nsp) del 1 del 1 del 1
del 1
l_geam=l_usa-2*x_profil_usa+0.03-0.04-0.013 g_geam=0.004
add2 -0.015+x_profil_usa,y_profil_usa-0.008 mul2 1,-1 GOSUB "geam" del 1 del 1 ENDIF
RETURN
"door4":
add2 l_usa,0 mul2 -1,1 GOSUB "door3" del 1 del 1
RETURN
"door":
!rect2 0,0,dx1_usa,g_usa
l1_prism=0.4 l2_prism=0.3 x_r_door=0.1 g_door=0.022 y1_prism=0.2 y2_prism=0.1 r_prism=0.003
l_prism=x_profil_usa g_profil=0.002 y_prism=y_profil_usa
IF (index_2d_level=1) THEN PUT 0,0,15, l_usa,0,15, l_usa,y_prism,15, 0,y_prism,15 poly2_B nsp/3,1+2+4,fill_p,fill_b,get(nsp) ENDIF
IF (index_2d_level=2) THEN add2 x_profil_usa,y_profil_usa/2 rot2 90 GOSUB "profil usa5 t" poly2_B nsp/3,1+2+4,fill_p,fill_b,get(nsp) del 2
add2 l_usa,y_profil_usa mul2 -1,-1 add2 x_profil_usa,y_profil_usa/2 rot2 90 GOSUB "profil usa6 t" poly2_B nsp/3,1+2+4,fill_p,fill_b,get(nsp) del 3
del 1
l_geam=l_usa-2*x_profil_usa+0.03 g_geam=0.004
add2 -0.015+x_profil_usa,y_profil_usa-0.008 mul2 1,-1 GOSUB "geam" del 2 ENDIF
RETURN
"geam":
set fill gs_fillLeaf
put 0,0,15, l_geam,0,15, l_geam,g_geam,15, 0,g_geam,15
poly2_B nsp/3,1+2+4,gs_penLeaf_fg,gs_penLeaf_bg,get(nsp)
add2 0,0.022 put 0,0,15, l_geam,0,15, l_geam,g_geam,15, 0,g_geam,15
poly2_B nsp/3,1+2+4,gs_penLeaf_fg,gs_penLeaf_bg,get(nsp) del 1
RETURN
"contur rama simpla":
PUT 0,0,15, l_prism,0,15, l_prism,y_prism-0.02,15, 0,y_prism-0.02,15
RETURN
"contur rama simpla2":
PUT 0,0,15, l_prism,0,15, l_prism,y_prism-0.02-0.014,15, 0,y_prism-0.02-0.014,15
RETURN
"contur profil Uu":
! l_prism latime profil, = x_rama ! y_prism inaltime profil, = y_rama ! gx_mij latime cuta mijloc ! gy_mij inaltime cuta mijloc ! g_profil grosime profil ! offx1 indoitura
put 0,0,15, l_prism,0,15, l_prism,y_prism1-g_profil,15, l_prism+0.01,y_prism1-g_profil,15, l_prism+0.01,y_prism,15, l_prism,y_prism,15, l_prism,y_prism-g_profil,15, l_prism+0.01-g_profil,y_prism-g_profil,15, l_prism+0.01-g_profil,y_prism1,15, l_prism/2+gx_mij/2,y_prism1,15, l_prism/2+gx_mij/2,y_prism1+gy_mij,15, l_prism/2-gx_mij/2,y_prism1+gy_mij,15, l_prism/2-gx_mij/2,y_prism1,15, 0,y_prism1,15
RETURN
"contur profil Uu2":
! l_prism latime profil, = x_rama ! y_prism inaltime profil, = y_rama ! gx_mij latime cuta mijloc ! gy_mij inaltime cuta mijloc ! g_profil grosime profil ! offx1 indoitura
put 0,0,15, l_prism,0,15, l_prism,y_prism1-g_profil,15, l_prism+0.01,y_prism1-g_profil,15, l_prism+0.01,y_prism,15, l_prism,y_prism,15, l_prism,y_prism-g_profil,15, l_prism+0.01-g_profil,y_prism-g_profil,15, l_prism+0.01-g_profil,y_prism1,15, l_prism/2+gx_mij/2,y_prism1,15, l_prism/2+gx_mij/2,y_prism1+gy_mij,15, l_prism/2-gx_mij/2,y_prism1+gy_mij,15, l_prism/2-gx_mij/2,y_prism1,15, 0,y_prism1,15
RETURN
"profil usa5 t":
put -l_prism/2,0,15, -l_prism/2+0.026,0,15, -l_prism/2+0.026,0.015,15, l_prism/2-0.008,0.015,15, l_prism/2-0.008,0,15, l_prism/2,0,15, l_prism/2,y_prism,15, l_prism/2-0.006,y_prism,15, l_prism/2-0.006,y_prism-0.02,15, -l_prism/2+0.006,y_prism-0.02,15, -l_prism/2+0.006,y_prism,15, -l_prism/2,y_prism,15
RETURN
"profil usa6 t":
put l_prism/2,0,15, l_prism/2-0.026,0,15, l_prism/2-0.026,0.015,15, -(l_prism/2-0.008),0.015,15, -(l_prism/2-0.008),0,15, -l_prism/2,0,15, -l_prism/2,y_prism,15, -0.03/2,y_prism,15, -0.03/2,y_prism+0.015,15, 0.03/2,y_prism+0.015,15, 0.03/2,y_prism,15, l_prism/2,y_prism,15
RETURN
"profil usa7 t":
put -l_prism/2,0,15, -l_prism/2+0.026,0,15, -l_prism/2+0.026,0.015,15, l_prism/2-0.008,0.015,15, l_prism/2-0.008,0,15, l_prism/2,0,15, l_prism/2,y_prism-0.02,15, l_prism/2-0.005,y_prism-0.02,15, l_prism/2-0.005,y_prism-0.03,15, l_prism/2-0.006,y_prism-0.03,15, -l_prism/2+0.006,y_prism-0.03,15, -l_prism/2+0.006,y_prism,15, -l_prism/2,y_prism,15
RETURN
Symbol.Script_3D:
IF volum_3d<>1 THEN END ENDIF define material "glass" 0, 0.4, 0.7, 0.8, !Surface RGB 0.95, 0.70, !ambient, diffuse 0.50, 0.60,!specular,ADDparent 50, !shining 0, !ADDparency attenuation 1, 1, 1,!Specular RGB 0.0, 0.0, 0.0, !Emission RGB 0.0 !Emission attenuation define material "alu" 0, 1, 0.95, 0.75, !Surface RGB 0.80, 0.10, !ambient, diffuse 0.70, 0.0,!specular,ADDparent 49, !shining 0, !ADDparency attenuation 1, 1, 1,!Specular RGB 0.0, 0.0, 0.0, !Emission RGB 0.0 !Emission attenuation define material "lemn" 3, 0.9, 0.7, 0.4 MULZ 1-2*(1-WIDO_REVEAL_SIDE) rotx -90 ADD -a/2,WALL_THICKNESS/2,0 MULY -(1-2*(1-WIDO_REVEAL_SIDE)) ADDY y_rama/2 GOSUB "handles" !!3D HANDLES MATERIAL gs_frame_mat GOSUB "rame" ADDZ h1_door mulz -1 !GOSUB "balama rama" del 1 del 1 muly -1 add x_rama-offset_pliere,0,x_profil_usa+sill*(x_rama - 0.02+offseth_prag) GOSUB "pliere" del 1 del 1 del 1 del 1 del 1 del 1 del 1 END "handles": ADDX x_rama unID=0 unID=unID+1 hotspot 0,0,0,unID,l1_pliat, 1+128 unID=unID+1 hotspot l1_pliat,0,0,unID,l1_pliat, 2 unID=unID+1 hotspot -1,0,0,unID,l1_pliat, 3 del 1 RETURN
"balama rama": h_balama=0.05 ADD 0.03 , 0.003 , 0.01 ROTZ 45 ADDX 0.012 CYLIND h_balama, 0.009 del 1 ADD 0.012,-0.006/2,0 MULX -1 BRICK 0.04, 0.012, h_balama del 1 del 1 ADD 0.012,0,h_balama/2-0.03/2 ROTZ u_diag-90 ADDy -0.006/2 BRICK 0.04, 0.012, 0.03 del 1 del 1 del 1 del 1 del 1 RETURN
"balama usa impar1": IF kk>1 AND kk<=n1 THEN GOSUB "balama usa" ADDz h1_door-x_profil_usa MULz -1 GOSUB "balama usa" del 1 del 1 ENDIF RETURN
"balama usa impar2": IF kk<n1 THEN ADDx dx1_usa MULy -1 GOSUB "balama usa2" ADDz h1_door-x_profil_usa MULz -1 GOSUB "balama usa2" del 1 del 1 del 1 del 1 ENDIF RETURN
"balama usa": h_balama=0.05 ADD 0 , -0.011, -x_profil_usa+0.01 CYLIND h_balama, 0.009 ROTZ 55-u_diag ADDy 0.003 MULy -1 BRICK 0.023, 0.012, h_balama del 1 del 1 del 1 ADDz h_balama/2-0.03/2 MULx -1 ROTZ 55-u_diag ADDy 0.003 MULy -1 BRICK 0.023, 0.012, h_balama del 1 del 1 del 1 del 1 del 1 del 1 RETURN
"balama usa2": h_balama=0.05 ADD -0.018 * sin(u_diag)/2, -y_profil_usa - 0.011 ,-x_profil_usa + 0.01 CYLIND h_balama, 0.009 ADDz h_balama/2-0.03/2 ROTZ (-u_diag*2-2*u_corectie-u_diff)*rot_panou+55 ADDy 0.003 MULy -1 BRICK 0.03, 0.012, h_balama del 1 del 1 del 1 del 1 MULx -1 ROTZ 55 ADDy 0.003 MULy -1 BRICK 0.021, 0.012, h_balama del 1 del 1 del 1 del 1 del 1 RETURN
"pliere": l_cadru = x_panou1 offsetx_balama = 0 offsety_balama = 0 kk = 0 !COUNT FOR ll = 0 TO l1_pliat-0.03 STEP dx1_pliat kk = kk+1 mm = CEIL ( FRA ( kk / 2 ) ) !MIRROR CHECKING ADDx ll IF mm THEN GOSUB "expresie usa nivel impar" ENDIF IF NOT ( mm ) THEN GOSUB "expresie usa nivel par" ENDIF del 1 NEXT ll RETURN
"expresie usa nivel impar": GOSUB "balama usa impar1" ADDx 0.018*sin(u_diag)/2 rotz (-u_diag)*rot_panou rotz (-u_corectie-u_diff*sin(u_diag))*rot_panou GOSUB "door1" GOSUB "balama usa impar2" del 1 del 1 del 1 RETURN
"expresie usa nivel par": ADDx dx1_pliat-0.018*sin(u_diag)/2 mulx -1 rotz (-u_diag)*rot_panou rotz (-u_corectie-u_diff*sin(u_diag))*rot_panou GOSUB "door2" del 1 del 1 del 1 del 1 RETURN
"rame": dim tip_prag[] tip_prag[1]="contur profil Uu" tip_prag[2]="prag intermediar" tip_prag[3]="flush sill" rama_stanga="contur profil Uu" rama_dreapta="contur profil Uu" rama_sus="contur profil Uu" prag=tip_prag[mm] l_prism=y_rama !profunzime rama y_prism=x_rama !latime rama y_prism1=x_rama-0.03 g_profil=0.002 g_prism=h_door gx_mij=0.045 gy_mij=0.015 g_prism=h_door h_offset_rama=h_door GOSUB "rama stanga" g_prism=x_door GOSUB "rama sus" g_prism=h_door GOSUB "rama dreapta" IF sill=1 THEN g_prism=x_door l_prism=l_prag y_prism=h_prag y_prism1=h1_prag gx_mij=gx_mij_prag gy_mij=gy_mij_prag Addz offseth_prag-h_perie GOSUB "prag" del 1 ENDIF RETURN
"rama stanga": Addz g_prism ROTy 45 cutplane 0 del 1 del 1 ROTz -90 GOSUB rama_stanga !!contur rama_stanga prism_ nsp/3,g_prism,get(nsp) del 1 cutend RETURN
"rama dreapta": Addx x_door mulx -1 GOSUB "rama stanga" del 1 del 1 RETURN
"rama sus": Addz h_offset_rama ROTy 45 cutplane 180 del 1 ADDX g_prism mulx -1 ROTy 45 cutplane 180 del 1 del 1 del 1 ROTy 90 ROTz -90 GOSUB rama_sus !!contur rama_sus prism_ nsp/3,g_prism,get(nsp) del 1 del 1 del 1 cutend cutend RETURN
"prag": ROTy -45 IF mm=1 THEN cutplane 0 ENDIF del 1 ADDX g_prism mulx -1 ROTy -45 IF mm=1 THEN cutplane 0 ENDIF del 1 del 1 del 1 muly -1 ROTy 90 ROTz 90 GOSUB prag !!contur prag prism_ nsp/3,g_prism,get(nsp) del 1 del 1 del 1 IF mm=1 THEN cutend cutend ENDIF RETURN
"door": l1_prism=-0.4 l2_prism=0.3 x_r_door=0.1 g_door=0.022 y1_prism=0.2 y2_prism=0.1 l_prism=x_profil_usa g_profil=0.002 y_prism=y_profil_usa h_cadru=h1_door offh1=0.03 gx_mij=0.012 gy_mij=0.015 gx2_mij=0.008 gy2_mij=0.022 MATERIAL gs_frame_mat ADDy g_usa/2 GOSUB "cadru usa" x_glas=l_usa-2*x_profil_usa h_glas=h_cadru-x_profil_usa+0.03 g_geam=0.003 GOSUB "geam" del 1 IF kk=n1 THEN ADD dx1_usa,0,offh_handle MULX -1 GOSUB "handle" del 1 del 1 ENDIF RETURN
"door1": l_usa = l_cadru tip_profil="profil usa5 t" tip_profil2="profil usa6 t" offset_profil2=0 IF kk=n1 THEN offset_profil2=0.04 l_usa = l_cadru - offset_profil2-0.013 tip_profil2="profil usa7 t" ENDIF ADDy y_profil_usa MULy -1 GOSUB "door" del 1 del 1 RETURN
"door2": l_usa = l_cadru tip_profil="profil usa5 t" tip_profil2="profil usa6 t" offset_profil2=0 ADDx x_panou1 MULX -1 IF kk=n1 THEN offset_profil2=0.04 l_usa = l_cadru - offset_profil2-0.013 tip_profil2="profil usa7 t" ENDIF ADDy y_profil_usa MULy -1 GOSUB "door" del 1 del 1 del 1 del 1 RETURN
"geam": MATERIAL mat_geam ADD x_profil_usa-0.015,g_geam/2-0.0185,-0.03/2 BRICK x_glas+0.03, g_geam, h_glas ADDy 0.016 MULy -1 BRICK x_glas+0.03, g_geam, h_glas del 1 del 1 del 1 MATERIAL gs_frame_mat RETURN
"cadru usa": g_prism=h_cadru ADDx y_prism ROTZ 90 GOSUB tip_profil n = nsp/3 PUT 0,-l_usa+2*y_prism,h_cadru/2-y_prism,0, 0,-l_usa+2*y_prism,h_cadru-y_prism,0, 0,0,h_cadru-y_prism,0, 0,0,0,0, 0,-l_usa+2*y_prism,0,0, 0,-l_usa+2*y_prism,h_cadru/2-y_prism,0
m = ( nsp - n * 3 ) / 4 TUBE n , m , 1 + 2+16+32 , GET ( n * 3 ) , GET ( m * 4 )
y_prism=y_profil_usa+offset_profil2 rama_panou_stanga=tip_profil2 h_prism=h_cadru+y_profil_usa ADD 0,-l_usa+2*y_profil_usa,-y_profil_usa MULY -1 GOSUB "rama stanga panou" del 1 del 1 del 1 del 1 RETURN
"rama stanga panou": ADDY y_profil_usa ROTz -90 ROTy -45 cutplane 180 del 1 ADDZ h_prism ROTy 45 cutplane 0 del 1 del 1 del 1 del 1 GOSUB rama_panou_stanga !!contur rama_stanga prism_ nsp/3,h_prism,get(nsp) cutend cutend RETURN
"contur profil Uu": PUT 0,0,15, l_prism,0,15, l_prism,y_prism1-g_profil,15, l_prism+0.01,y_prism1-g_profil,15, l_prism+0.01,y_prism,15, l_prism,y_prism,15, l_prism,y_prism-g_profil,15, l_prism+0.01-g_profil,y_prism-g_profil,15, l_prism+0.01-g_profil,y_prism1,15, l_prism/2+gx_mij/2,y_prism1,15, l_prism/2+gx_mij/2,y_prism1+gy_mij,15, l_prism/2-gx_mij/2,y_prism1+gy_mij,15, l_prism/2-gx_mij/2,y_prism1,15, 0,y_prism1,15
RETURN
"prag intermediar": PUT 0,0,15, l_prism,0,15, l_prism,y_prism-g_profil-0.02,15, l_prism-0.005/2,y_prism-g_profil-0.02,15, l_prism-0.005/2,y_prism-g_profil,15, l_prism+0.01,y_prism-g_profil,15, l_prism+offset_prag,y_prism1,15, l_prism+offset_prag+g_profil,y_prism1,15, l_prism+0.012,y_prism,15, l_prism/2+gx_mij/2,y_prism,15, l_prism/2+gx_mij/2,y_prism-gy_mij,15, l_prism/2-gx_mij/2,y_prism-gy_mij,15, l_prism/2-gx_mij/2,y_prism,15, l_prism/2-gx_mij/2-0.01,y_prism,15, l_prism/2-gx_mij/2-0.01,y_prism1,15, 0,y_prism1,15
RETURN
"flush sill": PUT 0,0,15, l_prism,0,15, l_prism,y_prism-g_profil,15, l_prism+offset_prag,y_prism-g_profil,15, l_prism+offset_prag,y_prism,15, l_prism/2+gx_mij/2,y_prism,15, l_prism/2+gx_mij/2,y_prism-gy_mij,15, l_prism/2-gx_mij/2,y_prism-gy_mij,15, l_prism/2-gx_mij/2,y_prism,15, -offset_prag,y_prism,15, -offset_prag,y_prism-g_profil,15, 0,y_prism-g_profil,15
RETURN
